      "description": "Presenting a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline mated to a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanical provenance is impeccable: the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rod bearing service is fully documented. The rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. Equipped with the factory M-Variable Differential Lock and a perfectly calibrated suspension, this specimen offers unparalleled steering feedback and chassis composure. No paint correction required; all VIN tags are present, and the undercarriage is free of oxidation.",
